<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="chat-n">chat <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tʃæt/    美 /tʃæt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 聊天；闲谈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have a chat</strong>
闲谈；聊天</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a chat show (BrE) / talk show (AmE )
访谈节目；脱口秀</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I enjoy a <strong>chat with</strong> a friend <strong>about</strong> football.
我喜欢与朋友聊足球。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I like to chat online and to meet new people in <strong>chat rooms</strong>.
我喜欢网上聊天，在聊天室结识新朋友。</p><footer>译林⑦ – 3</footer></div></div>